    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in total showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and feels brand new, this is the one for you! Come take a look and fall in love.",
